{
  "stem": "19198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their aim certainly was to exclude the Jews from all political, cultural, and commercial influence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- and their slogans certainly indicated that they wanted to eliminate the Jews period.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews, any-- anybody to the left of the center party or even the center party was not desirable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they-- it was very clear that Hitler's book, represented their party goals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One did not take them too seriously because they were still a minority, and even when they became a major party in the elections, the tendency was to laugh, rather than-- to laugh at them, rather than fear them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Nazis did take over, my father took a bet with a relative that they would be through within three or four months.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, he lost the bet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was certainly a different kind of a book, different from almost anything that had been written in the field, and because it was aimed directly at us as Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the extent that it did affect life in our town, yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I'm sure I didn't read it until I was in my teens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But by that time, that was 1928 and they were getting to be a power nationally, even though they had been a power in our town politically for some time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- one-- except during the time that they were prohibited from wearing their uniforms, you'd-- you'd see their uniforms constantly-- either individuals walking to a meeting or they would march with their drum and fife outfits all the time.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, once they took over, there was hardly a time when you didn't hear drums.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After all, it was known that I was a Jew and I wouldn't have been permitted anywhere near there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
